{
  "stem": "13395.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The bus and all traffic stopped, and everybody Sieg Heil and Sieg Heil, and saluting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I wasn't part of these people anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that I recall was the first time that I realized that I am different.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not even 10 yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Confusion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Knowing how my mother was loyal to the Kaiser and always hearing their conversation, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] and suddenly, I'm not part of these people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the first time I realized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, of course, German Jews, they were athletes, but they were not participating in the Olympics.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no-- no way they could participate in the Olympic games.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not have to ask, because I was always there when the conversations were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By that time already, you know, as I told you, many changes have taken place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, the Berlin Philharmonics, when you get a job as a musician, this is for life till your retirement.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All Jewish musicians were fired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the first time in the history of the Berlin Philharmonics that they would fire a musician.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all these-- and so what happened then, the Jewish community, because they couldn't attend theater, and because all these actors couldn't get a part in a play, they then had their own Jewish theaters.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then a Jewish cultural life began to flourish, which something terrible was happening, and it turned out to really awaken the Jewishness in-- in the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before it was only a religious affiliation where the German Jews were religiously Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they no longer were be able to find a position or a job, suddenly there was another side to their Jewishness, and they became culturally Jewish.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
